quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  12,21,"Soodu…óo mo on Misra wi'ani …ìeyngu makko: \"Teddin jipporde makko. Hino gasa ka o nafa en maa jogito…óe mo …ìi…ó…óo\". Ko nii Men ho…óniri Yuusufa ka leydi fii yo Men anndin mo firo koy…ói. Alla ko foolu…óo e fiyaaku Makko on: kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen anndaa"
  12,22,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko, Men okki mo faamu e anndal. Ko wano nii Men yo…ìirta mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  12,23,"On [debbo] mo on woni e suudu mun …óa…ì…ìiri mo hoore-makko. O soki baafe …óen o wi'i: \"Mi heblanii-mo-ma!\" O maaki: \"Moolaare Alla! Jey…óo lam on mo∆¥∆¥inii weerde am. Si ko woni, too√±oo…ìe …ìen maletaake"
  12,24,"Gom…óii [debbo] on himmanii oon. Kanko kadi o himmanayno mo si wanaa o yi'ii hujja Joomi makko on. Ko nii [Men gerdiri] fii yo Men yiltu mo e bone e pankare. Pellet ko o jeyaa…óo e jeyaa…ìe amen la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen"
  12,25,"∆Åe …ói…óo kala …ìe adondiri ka baafal, o seekiri dolokke oya on …ìaawo. ∆Åe tawi moodi makko ka baafal. [debbo] on wi'i: \"Ko hon…óum woni njo…ìdi on faalanaa…óo …ìeynguure maa nden bonki si wanaa yo soke [o leptiree] lepte muusu…óe"
  12,26,"[Yuusufu] maaki: \"Ko kanko …óa…ì…ìiri lam hoore-am\". Tawanoo…óo e yim…ìe [debbo] on seeditii: \"Si tawii dolokke mum on ko yeeso seekiraa, haray ko [debbo] on goongi, kanko [gorko] on ko jeyaa…óo e fenu…ìe …ìen"
  12,27,"Si tawii non dolokke makko on ka …ìaawo seekiraa, haray [debbo] on fenii, kanko [gorko] on ko o jeyaa…óo goongu…ìe …ìen"
  12,28,"Nde [moodi makko] yi'unoo dolokke on ko …ìaawo seekori, o wi'i: \"∆äum ko jeyaa…óum e pewje mon! Pellet pewje mon …óen ko haawnii…óe"
  12,29,"Yuusufa, …óuurno gaayi e …óum. An [debbo on], insinano junuubi(bakkaat) maa …óin; tawde pellet a jeyaama e woopu…ìe …ìen"